bin/
obj/*
**/obj/*
# SSRD's build pipeline runs `dotnet build --no-restore` and bails with
# NETSDK1004 when these NuGet hint files are missing. Freesnöw confirmed
# committing them works for other modules · these are the only obj/
# files we keep tracked.
!**/obj/project.assets.json
!**/obj/project.nuget.cache
!**/obj/*.nuget.dgspec.json
!**/obj/*.nuget.g.props
!**/obj/*.nuget.g.targets
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
